title: Carroll Chamber honors businesses, leaders
maintext: The Carroll County Chamber of Commerce recently its annual awards banquet at General Butler State Resort Park in Carrollton. Jimmy Supplee was awarded the Raymond Ray Community Service Award, Tandy-Eckler-Riley Funeral Home was awarded the Beautification Award and the Carrollton Main Street Program received the Community Impact Award. Additionally, a silent auction during the event raised money for four scholarships to be given to local high school students.
